### **Critical Fixes (Must Do)**

1. **Parse Dictionary Correctly** — Don't hardcode. Read `lineitem_dicts.txt`, parse code-to-value mapping in order of appearance.
2. **Optimize Delta Decode** — Current O(n²) complexity per morsel. Store last-decoded value, use as starting point for next morsel (O(n) instead).

